title: Porcupine Tree - Deadwing (MP3 @ 320 kbps)
description:
Deadwing is the eighth studio album by British progressive rock band Porcupine Tree, released on 28 March 2005. It quickly became the band's best selling album, though was later surpassed by Fear of a Blank Planet. The album is based on a screenplay written by Steven Wilson and Mike Bennion, and is essentially a ghost story.

I snatched the discography from this site and noticed the volume cuts out quite badly on Deadwing.. I bought the disc myself and uploaded it. Enjoy!
